{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day01.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime11","chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm sorry...@About what happened in the last loop.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You don't need to apologize."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We were able to make note of events@that happen later on the flowchart,@so it wasn't for nothing."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I didn't want to kill Sayaka Miki@if I could help it, either."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So...what should we do now?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Are we going to have to start plotting@to stop Miss Miki from contracting too...?"},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I considered that, but it's not@a very realistic prospect."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If we keep looping, we may be able to@find a way to stop Kyubey ahead of time..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But I'd prefer not to see Madoka@suffer over and over again."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I agree with that, but then...@What are we supposed to do?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There's no need to complicate things."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We'll go with the same plan as before."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104206/vo_full_907101-030-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The same...as before?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
